  "title": "Newsletter & Marketing Email Filter",
  "description": "Automatically detect newsletter and marketing emails using a combination of header analysis (List-Unsubscribe header presence) and Claude classification. Detected newsletters are moved to a dedicated Newsletter folder and excluded from the main inbox by default. Users can whitelist specific senders.",
